      "type": "articles",
      "specificArticles": [
        {
          "textContent": "A trail along our favorite area, 'Tarina' land, where you will see some of the most spectacular landscapes. 'Tarina' land is pretty close to the historical center and here are the farmlands of the locals where they keep their animals or vegetable crops. The trail will take you to 'Țarina' lake and then to the Weather Station (on the top of Rosia Montana) where you will have a spectacular view. On the second part of the trail will descend along the 'Tăul Mare' lake and just before arriving in the historical center, you will make a stop at 'Văidoaia' Gallery and a very special old house 'Casa Szekely'.",
